'''奧馬·沙里夫'''（{{lang-en|Omar Sharif}}，{{lang-ar|عمر الشريف}}，{{bd|1932年|4月10日|2015年|7月10日|catIdx=S}}），又譯作'''奧馬·莎李夫'''，本名'''米歇尔·德米特里·薛胡布'''（Michel Demitri Chalhoub），埃及演員。其姓氏「沙里夫」（Sharif）在阿拉伯語裡有著「名貴」的意思。代表作品包含《[[阿拉伯的劳伦斯_(电影)|阿拉伯的勞倫斯]]》（1962）、《[[日瓦戈医生_(电影)|齊瓦哥醫生]]》（1966），以及《{{tsl|en|Funny Girl (film)|妙女郎}}》（1968）。其演藝成就曾為其博得[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]提名，並讓他摘下三座[[金球獎|金球獎]]與一座[[凯撒电影奖|凯撒电影奖]]。

== 早期生活 ==
奧馬·沙里夫，1932年4月10日<ref name=folmref>{{cite web | url = http://www.filmreference.com/film/44/Omar-Sharif.html | title = Omar Sharif Biography (1932-) | publisher = FilmReference.com | accessdate = May 25, 2015 | archive-date = 2020-09-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200915171517/http://www.filmreference.com/film/44/Omar-Sharif.html | dead-url = no }} Source notes: "Original name, Michael Shalhoub (some sources spell surname "Chalhoub")"</ref>生於[[埃及王國|埃及]][[亚历山大港|亚历山大港]]<ref name="Independent">[http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/omar-sharif-it-is-a-great-film-but-im-not-very-good-in-it-8326440.html "Omar Sharif: 'It is a great film, but I'm not very good in it'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/omar-sharif-it-is-a-great-film-but-im-not-very-good-in-it-8326440.html |date=20140122115644 }}, ''[[The_Independent|The Independent]]''</ref>，本名米歇爾·德米崔·薛胡布（Michel Demetri Chalhoub）<ref name=muslim-encyclopedia>{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=owZCMZpYamMC&pg=PA198&dq=omar+sharif+michel&hl=en&sa=X&ei=lq9jVdT1IYqqyQSnlIGQCQ&ved=0CCsQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=omar%20sharif%20michel&f=false | title=Encyclopedia of Muslim-American History | first=Edward E. | last=Curtis | page=198 | publisher=[[Facts_on_File|Facts on File]] | year=2010 | isbn=978-0816075751 | access-date=2015-07-10 | archive-date=2019-05-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519174852/https://books.google.com/books?id=owZCMZpYamMC&pg=PA198&dq=omar+sharif+michel&hl=en&sa=X&ei=lq9jVdT1IYqqyQSnlIGQCQ&ved=0CCsQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=omar%20sharif%20michel&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>，是具有[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]、[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]與[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]血統的[[默基特希臘禮天主教會|默基特希臘禮天主教徒]]家庭成員<ref name="Variety Jul 10">{{cite web | url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/omar-sharif-dead-lawrence-of-arabia-dr-zhivago-1201537607/ | title=<nowiki>Omar Sharif, ‘Lawrence of Arabia’ and ‘Dr. Zhivago’ Star, Dies at 83</nowiki> | publisher=Variety | date=10 July 2015 | accessdate=10 July 2015 | author=Dagan, Carmel; Weissber, Jay | archive-date=2021-01-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125020713/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/omar-sharif-dead-lawrence-of-arabia-dr-zhivago-1201537607/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。其父-{zh-cn:约瑟夫;zh-tw:約瑟夫;zh-hk:祖瑟夫;}-·薛胡布（Joseph Chalhoub）生於黎巴嫩，家族靠經營進口[[木材|木材]]起家，[[20世紀初期|20世紀初期]]舉家搬遷到[[埃及|埃及]]，且就是奧馬出生長大的地方。其母克萊兒·莎達（Claire Saada）則是敘利亞與黎巴嫩後裔<ref name="BBC obit">{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-26277821 | title=Obituary: Omar Sharif | publisher=BBC | date=10 July 2015 | accessdate=10 July 2015 | archive-date=2019-05-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190526002414/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-26277821 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。沙里夫青年時期，曾就讀於{{tsl|en|Victoria College, Alexandria|維多利亞學院 (亞歷山卓)|維多利亞學院}}，並展現了語言長才；畢業於開羅大學，並擁有[[數學|數學]]與[[物理|物理]]學學位<ref name="BBC obit"/>。1955年，沙里夫[[改宗|改宗]][[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.celebatheists.com/wiki/Omar_Sharif|title=Omar Sharif|publisher=|accessdate=10 July 2015|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225074242/https://www.celebatheists.com/wiki/Omar_Sharif|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以便娶埃及女演員[[法婷·哈馬瑪|法婷·哈馬瑪]]（Faten Hamama）為妻<ref>Sharif, Omar (1977), The Eternal Male: My Own Story, Doubleday, NY, 1st Ed., p. 71.</ref>。

在[[开罗大学|开罗大学]]獲得數學與物理學學位之後<ref name=Irish/>，他為父親經營的木材行業短暫工作過，隨後便進入位在[[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[皇家戏剧艺术学院|皇家戏剧艺术学院]]就讀表演相關科系<ref name=Irish>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/omar-sharif-from-desert-prince-to-alone-in-paris-1.1787034|title=Omar Sharif: from desert prince to alone in Paris|work=The Irish Times|date=May 8, 2014|accessdate=July 10, 2015|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303050743/https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/omar-sharif-from-desert-prince-to-alone-in-paris-1.1787034|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 演員生涯 ==
因演出《[[日瓦戈医生_(电影)|齊瓦哥醫生]]》(Doctor Zhivago)聞名全球。1962年演出《[[阿拉伯的劳伦斯_(电影)|阿拉伯的勞倫斯]]》(Lawrence of Arabia)，獲得金球獎最佳男配角。1966年演出《齊瓦哥醫生》，獲金球獎最佳男主角。2003年演出《陪我走到世界盡頭》，則讓莎李夫獲得凯撒电影奖最佳男主角獎。

== 合約橋牌生涯 ==
沙里夫曾名列世界前50大[[合約橋牌|合約橋牌]]玩家，並曾經在[[伊朗國王|伊朗國王]]面前打過牌<ref name="wapo">"<nowiki>Omar Sharif, international heartthrob of ‘Lawrence of Arabia’ and ‘Doctor Zhivago,’ dies at 83</nowiki>", Adam Bernstein, 10 July 2015, [http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/omar-sharif-international-heartthrob-of-lawrence-of-arabia-and-doctor-zhivago-dies-at-83/2015/07/10/10016f80-270a-11e5-b72c-2b7d516e1e0e_story.html Washington Post] {{Wayback|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/omar-sharif-international-heartthrob-of-lawrence-of-arabia-and-doctor-zhivago-dies-at-83/2015/07/10/10016f80-270a-11e5-b72c-2b7d516e1e0e_story.html |date=20201117081206 }}''</ref>。沙里夫也曾與{{tsl|en|Charles Goren|查爾斯·葛倫}}共同為《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》寫過好幾年的橋牌專欄<ref>{{cite news | url=http://blogs.chicagotribune.com/news_columnists_ezorn/2005/09/bridges_to_the_.html | work=Chicago Tribune | title=Change of Subject – Observations, reports, tips, referrals and tirades  Chicago Tribune  Blog | date=6 September 2005 | accessdate=2015-07-10 | archive-date=2011-09-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928104133/http://blogs.chicagotribune.com/news_columnists_ezorn/2005/09/bridges_to_the_.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但大多數的寫作之後都轉手給[[譚納·赫希|譚納·赫希]]（Tannah Hirsch）。他也是好幾本橋牌相關書籍的作者與共同作者，甚至授權其名給一個橋牌電視遊戲；更是被选为世界桥牌协会会长，最一開始只在1992年發行了[[MS-DOS|MS-DOS]]與[[Amiga|Amiga]]版本，《奧馬·沙里夫打橋牌》（Omar Sharif in Bridge）至今也仍在[[Windows|Windows]]與行動平台版本販售<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thetradingcentre.co.uk/products.asp?category=Omar+Sharif+Bridge |title=> {subcategory} |publisher=Thetradingcentre.co.uk |accessdate=18 November 2012}}</ref>。《[[電腦遊戲世界|電腦遊戲世界]]》雜誌1992年時曾評論這個遊戲「好上手、難挑戰、設計佳」（easy to get into, challenging to play and well-designed）<ref name="wilson199209">{{cite news | url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1992&pub=2&id=98 | title=Interplay's Omar Sharif on Bridge | work=Computer Gaming World | date=September 1992 | accessdate=3 July 2014 | author=Wilson, Johnny L. | pages=20–21 | archive-date=2014-07-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702235436/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1992&pub=2&id=98 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並將它列名為當年度最棒的策略遊戲<ref name="cgwgoty199211">{{cite news | url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1992&pub=2&id=100 | title=CGW Salutes The Games of the Year | work=Computer Gaming World | date=November 1992 | accessdate=4 July 2014 | pages=110 | archive-date=2014-07-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702235552/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1992&pub=2&id=100 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。但1993年，該雜誌指出「這不是一個玩橋牌的好遊戲」，因其文檔不足、玩家無法適應而遭受批評。該雜誌甚至推薦了另外兩款遊戲<ref name="lindeman199303">{{cite news | url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1993&pub=2&id=104 | title=Three Top Computer Bridge Games | work=Computer Gaming World | date=March 1993 | accessdate=6 July 2014 | author=Lindeman, David E. | pages=42 | archive-date=2014-07-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702235803/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1993&pub=2&id=104 | dead-url=no }}</ref> <!-- hide unrefernced material For a number of years his partner at international tournaments was Egyptian contract bridge superstar Maged Elewa.-->。

沙里夫是法國賭場的常客<ref>"Omar Sharif sued for assault". (6 November 2005). ''[[New_Straits_Times|New Sunday Times]]'', p. 29.</ref>。

== 私人生活 ==
=== 疾病與死亡 ===
2015年5月，報載沙里夫飽受[[阿兹海默病|-{zh-cn:阿兹海默病; zh-tw:阿茲海默症; zh-hk:認知障礙症;}-]]所苦，據其子轉述，沙里夫已經開始認不清楚其演藝生涯的幾部代表作品。其子塔里克·沙里夫是沙里夫與前妻法婷·哈馬瑪的獨子，他表示自己父親總把這些電影的名字搞混，甚至忘記《齊瓦哥醫生》、《阿拉伯的勞倫斯》的拍攝地點<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3094189/Legendary-actor-Omar-Sharif-Alzheimer-s-disease-confuses-starring-roles-Doctor-Zhivago-Lawrence-Arabia.html | work=DailyMail | title=Legendary actor Omar Sharif 'has Alzheimer's disease and confuses his starring roles in Doctor Zhivago and Lawrence of Arabia' | date=May 23, 2015 | accessdate=July 10, 2015 | archive-date=2016-07-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720191636/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3094189/Legendary-actor-Omar-Sharif-Alzheimer-s-disease-confuses-starring-roles-Doctor-Zhivago-Lawrence-Arabia.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年7月10日，因[[心臟病|心臟病]]發，病逝於開羅一家醫院，享壽83歲<ref>{{cite news|title=<nowiki>Omar Sharif, a Star in ‘Dr. Zhivago,’ Dies at 83</nowiki>|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/11/movies/omar-sharif-a-star-in-dr-zhivago-dies-at-83.html|accessdate=July 10, 2015|work=New York Times website|date=July 10, 2015|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308150958/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/11/movies/omar-sharif-a-star-in-dr-zhivago-dies-at-83.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/PA/status/619503999851589632|title=Press Association on Twitter|work=Twitter|accessdate=10 July 2015|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210023940/https://twitter.com/PA/status/619503999851589632|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

